word_mean_info__list.difference: 即可指法律性文件，也可指用作证明或消息来源的文件或记录等。
普通用词，泛指成册供将来参考或使用的任何文件或公文等。
多指在报刊、杂志上发表的非文艺性的文章，包括新闻报导、学术论文等。
正式用词，多指在学术刊物上发表或在学术会议上宣读的专题论文，也指高等学校的学期论文，或学校里的作文练习。
一般指大学或高中生作为作业所写的篇幅有限、较完整论述某个观点的文章。也可指作品或谈话的主要论题。
多指学校里老师给学生的作文练习。
书面语用词，指独立研究后所写的较为详细的专题文章；也可指学位论文。
指任何一种非小说性的，篇幅不长、结构简练的文章，如论说文、报道、评论、讽刺性杂文等。
既可指毕业论文、学位论文，又可指一般的为阐述学术观点而写的论文。

yingyinNormal.en: Can we make an aeroplane that flies? Yes, all we need is some paper. We know where there is paper. There is lots of old paper in the workroom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们是不是做一架能飞的飞机啊。当然，只要一些纸就能做啊。我们知道哪里可以找到纸。工作室里有很多用过的纸。

yingyinNormal.en: Can we make an aeroplane that flies? Yes, all we need is some paper. We know where there is the paper. There is lots of old paper in the workroom.

yingyinNormal.en: I thought it was paper cuts, but I was wrong. No piece of paper ever cut me this deep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我本以为就像被纸割到手，但我错了，从没有一张纸比女人割我还深。

yingyinNormal.en: My job is all about numbers. I take very important pieces of paper. I take a rubber stamp, and I stamp the paper.

yingyinNormal.zh: 我的工作都是跟数字有关的，我会拿一张非常重要的纸，就像这样，我还要一个印章，然后我要在纸上盖章。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's some paper. Perfect. Mummy Pig is going to make a paper aeroplane.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，纸来了。非常好。祝妈妈现在准备给大家做一架纸飞机。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's some paper. Perfect. Mummy Pig is going to make a paper aeroplane.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，纸来了。非常好。祝妈妈现在准备给大家做一架纸飞机。

yingyinNormal.en: Unless, of course, the piece of paper was a hundred dollar bill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除非那张纸是一张百元大钞。

yingyinNormal.zh: 除非那张纸是一张百元大钞。

yingyinNormal.en: I got air in my lungs and a few blank sheets of paper.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有个健康的身体，以及作画用的纸。

yingyinNormal.en: Ross. Are there naked chicks on that piece of paper? No. Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 罗斯，你那张纸上有裸女吗？没有，怎么了？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I thought so to until I paper mached one of my eyes shut.

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.zh: 论文; 报告; 文件

examination_example.sentence: With the content of <highlight>papers</highlight> secured for free, the publisher needs only find a market for its journal.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 由于论文的内容是免费的，出版商只需要为其期刊找到一个市场。

examination_example.sentence: Companies located in places with happier people invest more, according to a recent research <highlight>paper</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近的一份研究报告显示，公司所在地的居民越快乐，公司的投资就越多。

examination_example.sentence: Analyses reveal that the number of <highlight>papers</highlight> including the keywords "environmental change" or "climate change" have increased rapidly since 2004.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 分析显示，自2004年以来，包含“环境变化”或“气候变化”关键词在内的论文数量迅速增加。

examination_example.sentence: Nostalgia for ink on <highlight>paper</highlight> and the rustle of pages aside, there's plenty of incentive to ditch print.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 抛开对纸上油墨和书页沙沙声的怀念，放弃印刷的动机很充足。

examination_example.sentence: Second, <highlight>paper</highlight> checks have the advantage that they provide receipts, something that many consumers are unwilling to give up.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 其次，纸质支票的优点是提供收据，这是许多消费者不愿放弃的。

examination_example.sentence: Now think of your laptop, thinner than a brown-<highlight>paper</highlight> envelope, or your cellphone in the palm of your hand.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在想一想你那比牛皮纸信封还薄的笔记本电脑，或是握在手中的手机。

examination_example.sentence: "Sometime in the future," the <highlight>paper</highlight>'s publisher said back in 2010.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该报的出版商曾在2010年说道：“在未来的某个时候。”

examination_example.sentence: To expand the popularity of the <highlight>paper</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 扩大报纸的知名度。

word_usage.usage: on paper表示“以书面形式”或“理论上”。

paper, article, essay, composition都可表示“文章”：
paper多指在学术刊物上发表的专题论文。
article指在报刊、杂志上发表的结构完整的文章。
essay指除小说、诗歌之外的，篇幅较短的文章。
composition指条理清楚、内容完整的文章，多指学生的作文。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 指毕业论文、学位论文等。
指文学上的和哲学上的论文。
篇幅最长，学术含量高，多指经过一定调查与实践后所写的专题论文。

examination_example.sentence: A 2006 research <highlight>paper</highlight> suggested some correlation between the amount of homework done by a student and future academic achievement.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2006年的一篇研究论文表明，学生的家庭作业量与未来的学业成绩之间存在一定的相关性。

examination_example.sentence: A recent <highlight>paper</highlight> claimed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近的一篇论文声称。

examination_example.sentence: What did a recent research <highlight>paper</highlight> claim?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近的一篇研究论文声称什么？

examination_example.sentence: Yet the <highlight>paper</highlight> does say children are "unintentionally genetically selected" by the school system.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，这篇论文确实指出，孩子们是被学校系统“无意的基因选择”的。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 研究论文；研究报告；调研报告

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Paper</highlight> and plastic toys were the items removed next most from noses.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 纸和塑料玩具是从鼻子上取下最多的物品。

examination_example.sentence: To promote the use of <highlight>paper</highlight> bags for shopping.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 推广使用纸袋购物。

examination_example.sentence: Today, Americans are finding their own tips and tricks for fixing malfunctioning devices with supplies as simple as <highlight>paper</highlight> and glue.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今天，美国人正在寻找他们自己的小窍门，用纸和胶水这样简单的东西来修理出故障的设备。

examination_example.sentence: A research <highlight>paper</highlight> rejected by one journal may get accepted by another.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 被一家期刊拒绝的一篇研究性论文可能会被另一家期刊接受。

examination_example.sentence: He wanted to "prove to the distant future that the French chefs of the 19th century were the most famous in the world," as he wrote in his <highlight>papers</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 正如他在论文中所写的那样，他希望“向遥远的未来证明19世纪的法国厨师是世界上最出名的”。

examination_example.sentence: But the new <highlight>paper</highlight> suggests that if you want long life, you should strive to be as outgoing as possible.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但这篇新发表的论文建议，如果你想长寿，你应该努力尽可能地开朗些。
